{
  "stem": "9168.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- I went to this synagogue alone at night to see this film.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have never seen that film anywhere since.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was of the ovens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I just remember that the mothers being sent to the ovens with the babies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now this may have been-- I don't know whether this was part of Mengele's work at Auschwitz, or what the origin of the film was, but it was film from Nazi Germany.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember the mothers alive being strapped to the oven cots that they slid in and out, and the babies being strapped to them, so that the live baby was over the live mother, strapped.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that the person in charge of the ovens, in this case, opened the oven door, and flames shot out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they pushed the cot with the living mother and baby into the flames alive and slammed the door shut.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And after that, you know, I mean I was just continually with [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] some terrible kind of suffering.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was all part of this horror story for me to eventually start speaking on this subject.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it seemed as though all the years after that I was busy raising two children, traveling with my military officer husband to various bases in the United States, you know.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But eventually became so active in speaking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "End of tape five.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
